# 🎨 Artista Shop - Art Gallery E-commerce

> Full-stack e-commerce platform for artists to sell original artworks online

![Demo Screenshot](screenshot.png)

## 🚀 Features

- Browse artwork gallery with filters
- Secure checkout with Stripe
- User authentication (JWT)
- Order management
- Responsive design

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

**Backend:** Django 4.x, Django REST Framework, PostgreSQL  
**Frontend:** React 18, Redux Toolkit, TailwindCSS  
**Payment:** Stripe API  
**Deploy:** Railway (backend), Vercel (frontend)

